Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:01:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# The impregnable fortress, G8! #
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# Pirates can't come near it! #
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# With its 108 cannons jutting out, #
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# it's a hedgehog that protects the peace! #
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# Our pride, G8! #
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, though, I hear our fortress\Nisn't very popular lately within the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I hear there're\Nsome people who call us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dim-witted hedgehogs made\Nsoft by peace behind our back...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not surprising, since we've had hardly\Nany pirate attacks the past few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me who said that.\NIt's a rumor! A rumor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! What's their problem?!\NPeace is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with peace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:03:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# The impregnable fortress, G8! #
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day is a beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, they really tore up this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably take at least a week to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our orders are to fix it in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did this ship climb a mountain or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Mechao-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good way of putting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it'd have to climb a mountain\Nor something to get this wrecked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, it might've\Nfallen from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably got caught around the\Nsea gate when entering the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that area is very narrow,\Nso it's hard to pass through,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even for a navigator who's used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's stop joking around\Nand get to work already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... Sailors these days don't\Nhave enough love for their ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Mechao-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A State of Emergency Is Issued!\NA Notorious Pirate Ship Has Infiltrated!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It appears that we've been invaded\Nby a huge object from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An invasion from the sky?!\NF-From the sky, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:20.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An unidentified mysterious\Nobject has invaded the base!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Guard the sea gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go watch the coast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sniper Unit! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close the sea gate!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there! 4 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4 o'clock! All lights on the target!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pirate ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate flag has... a skull with a straw hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Straw Hat Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target the Straw Hat Pirates' ship!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did somebody say "Straw Hat"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Commander Drake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship that has invaded our base\Nis the Straw Hat Pirates' ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, you say?!\NWhere's Commander Jonathan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... we can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, that man's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be damned... To think that\Nsomeone invaded from the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resistance is futile! We have\Nyou completely surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Full of Power!"\N"Carbohydrates!"\N"Navy Dining Hall"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's been pretty noisy outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wonder if there're\Nintruders or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No chit-chatting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! We have to prepare\Nmeals for 1,000 people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In two hours, a bunch of boys\Nfrom the night shift will show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time for fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But...\N--The siren from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, lads!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day this fortress falls\Nis the day the world falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, when Jessica-sama\Nblows up, she's a lot scarier than...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jessica-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! Where have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't catch anything today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had a large catch yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about that!\NCommander, if you're always absent...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal? Night fishing\Nisn't necessarily a waste, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, I have a report!\NAccording to the watchmen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the maintenance men inside\Nthe dock who saw the ship close by...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-According to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spit it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... well... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say they saw ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, something\Nsuddenly fell from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hairy monster appeared.\NIt jumped and then disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hands... Hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hands grew out from my body, and the\Nnext moment, everything went black!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... they were a girl's soft hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotta be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost ship!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't be ridiculous!\N--Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without doubt, that is the Straw Hats' ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way it's a ghost ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, of all things,\Nto say that it fell from the sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:10:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... the part about it coming\Nfrom the sky, at least, is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that it isn't a waste, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Lt. Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost ship, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! I found\Nthese in one of the rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ingots and a crown... Those are quite old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must've stolen them\Nfrom some ancient ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Send them to the forensics lab!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's explore inside, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chirps?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one. It's just an ordinary\NSouth Bird. There's nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--South Bird?\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a funny bird valued highly by old-time\Nsailors because they always point south.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:11:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're surprisingly violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're well maintained.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Medical books and history books... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess these ghosts study a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts again? How ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work. Continue\Nthe investigation of this ghost ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost ship, he says?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Got that?\N--Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that that ship\Nstopped by Jaya quite recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The coffee was tasty, wasn't it?\N--Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The color and smell of the\Ncoffee left on the deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was definitely Jaya Coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've got the courage to drink\Nit without investigating it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that South Bird... That's a bird\Nthat inhabits the jungles of Jaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know? A legend of gold\Nremains deeply entrenched there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, then that ship is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about its crew's whereabouts,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's certain that it came from Jaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not some ghost ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I've seen that ship twice.\NIt's the Straw Hats' ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you, yourself, called it a\Nghost ship earlier, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have fresh recruits\Nand prisoners at this fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we tell everyone about\Nthe Straw Hats' invasion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without knowing their true purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll only cause confusion\Nwithin the fortress, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's just keep calling\Nit a ghost ship for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all due respect, Commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should organize a special\Ninvestigation unit right away
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and search for them as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please assign it to my unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now, don't be so hasty.\N--But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Building up our defense is the priority now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go reinforce security at the coast\Nas well as around the sea gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go reinforce security at the\Nammunition bunker, detention facilities
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the major passageways. I'll also\Ngrant you authority to manage personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You look dissatisfied, Lt. Commander.\N--No, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The night is still long.\NThey probably can't move around much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that goes for us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait until morning, then take your unit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thoroughly investigate\Nplaces where people gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Places where people gather, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to find green insects since\Nthey live in green grassy places.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Straw Hats were to wear our uniforms...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't trust my men's abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's very possible that they'll\Ntake some of our uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:15:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are like stray dogs...\NThey're always hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you start by checking\Nthe dining hall once morning comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did everyone go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing we've got a waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Security is tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better get out of here right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me! This is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well... We've fallen\Nto a troublesome place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Nami-san and Robin-chan\Nwere able to escape okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's the matter?!\N--Well, I saw some sort of light in the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were probably seeing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even smoke in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beef, pork, chicken, beef, fish, pork...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat! Meat! Meat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how I look at it, I haven't\Neaten since we left the sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that didn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Chopper were here, he would've\Ncaught the smell of food for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... We can't even get\Nclose to the Merry like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreja Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all that, we couldn't find\Neven a single crewmember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even worse, the maintenance guys\Nsaid they saw monsters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and the Commander clearly\Nadmitted that this is a ghost ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How mean... asking us to\Nwatch a creepy ship like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:18:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Apparently, the Navy thinks\Nthat the Merry is a ghost ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost ship?! How rude! I'm gonna sue!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's better for us, as well as for\Nthe Merry, if they think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can buy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! They must've stolen\Ncursed gold from some ruins!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! I touched that gold...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gh-Ghost!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy and Pirate Hunter Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can probably assume that\Nthe woman with countless hands
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the hairy monster\Nare also part of the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, there're seven of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among them are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A skilled cook...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A knowledgeable ship's doctor...\NThere may be a historian as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a suspicious noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on! How do\Nthese convoluted hallways work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trapped! What am I gonna do?!\NWhat am I gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do?!\NWhat the heck should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's downstairs!\N--Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... where should I head?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought...\NIt's surrounded by land in all directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean we fell on a\Nhuge lake with no way out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, obtaining the information\Nwe need to escape is our top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be resolved... Long-nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot! He's got no sense of tension!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I don't know is their purpose.\NWhat on earth did they come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at any rate, my fortress\Nis no laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get moving towards the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move ahead, pursuing our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the answers are right here, pouring out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rush forth, rush forth,\Non the road opened before us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep moving forward! We can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't give in, we won't give in,\Neven if the obstacle is big
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to be scared of,\Nwe can overcome it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all places, this is a Navy fortress?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything until\Nwe know the entire picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.55,0:23:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see your cook's spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.06,0:23:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.39,0:23:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the fortress of Navarone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sanji the Cook! Proving His\NMerit at the Navy Dining Hall!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
